products.name: Men's Tech Shell Full-zip
products.description: A versatile full-zip that you can wear all day long and even to the gym. This technical shell features moisture-wicking fabric, added stretch and a hidden pocket for your smartphone or media player.
products.features:
• 100% polyester.
  • Smooth, technical front with textured mesh back.
  • Drawstring bottom for adjustable fit.
  • Raglan sleeves.
  • Available in forest green with the white Google logo embroidered at left chest.
